E-bill Relationship Management Project (EBRMP). EBRMP is a SaaSOPT smart biller that store bills of utilities data from multiple companies on a single platform to make life easier for utilities customers. The project was lead by Ebonmart Inc with joint partnership with Tet alone corporation along with funding from US Agency for international development (USAID).

Apart from EBRMP program, paucity study on Economic Development and Social Indicators from the year of 2015 to 2016 also taken place. In addition to that, D Disse to Residents (DBOR) was also successfully teseted and executed. This project was directly implemented by Tet alone Corporation with partners Ebonmart Inc and Pacific Communique Group.

Similar to the thing been made earlier, Marshall Islands also made actions in sanitation project information system(SAPSIS) where Smartwaste Management (SWM) was launch and Pacific Tele Center was officially closed down. Meanwhile, the project of Improving Red Cross Pacific Islands(NSRT) successfully carried out by Ebonmart Inc, Tet alone government and a leading training institute PTETA (Pacific Training and Education Technological Center).
